            <title>[LU-11776] add &quot;lfs find&quot; support for directory hash flags</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11776</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add support to &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs find -H&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; for finding directories with the &lt;tt&gt;migrating&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;dead&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;bad_type&lt;/tt&gt;, and &lt;tt&gt;lost_lmv&lt;/tt&gt; flags set.  These are added in &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33843&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33843&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11753&quot; title=&quot;MDS BUG on lfs migrate [osd_it_ea_rec]&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11753&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11753&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; utils: print out DNE2 directory hash flags&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
